parameters.text:
=Classify this AOL IMAP email as spam or not spam using retrieved Qdrant memory when relevant.

Mailbox: {{$json.sourceMailbox || ""}}
From: {{$json.From || $json.from || ""}}
Subject: {{$json.Subject || $json.subject || ""}}
Snippet: {{$json.snippet || ""}}
Labels: {{JSON.stringify($json.labels || [])}}

If Qdrant memory contains relevant past spam indicators, incorporate them into the decision.

Return ONLY valid JSON with this exact schema:
{
  "verdict": "SPAM" or "NOT_SPAM",
  "reason": "short reason",
  "memory_used": true or false
}

